---
layout: base.njk
title: AI Harness - A catalog of everything built around AI
description: "AI Harness: The model is commodity. The harness is the differentiator. A pattern catalog for builders, PMs, and leaders."
---

<div class="section-hero">
  <div class="dictionary-entry">
    <h1 class="dictionary-word">AI Harness</h1>
    <div class="dictionary-meta">
      <span class="dictionary-phonetic">/ey-eye hahr-nis/</span>
      <span class="dictionary-pos">noun</span>
    </div>
    <ol class="dictionary-defs">
      <li>{{ harness.definition }}</li>
      <li>The layer that determines whether an AI model becomes a chatbot, a search engine, a code editor, or an autonomous agent.</li>
    </ol>
    <p class="dictionary-example">"{{ harness.thesis }}"</p>
  </div>
</div>

<nav class="pattern-index">
  <h2 class="pattern-index-title">Architecture Categories</h2>
  <p class="pattern-index-subtitle">13 categories of architecture patterns that shape how AI products are built. Each describes a distinct way of wrapping a model to create useful software.</p>
  <ul class="pattern-index-list">
    {% for cat in harness.categories %}
    <li><a href="#{{ cat.id }}">{{ cat.name }}</a></li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</nav>

<div class="section">
  <ul class="section-list">
    {% for cat in harness.categories %}
    <li class="card" id="{{ cat.id }}">
      <a href="{{ ('/pattern/' + cat.id + '/') | url }}" class="card-link" aria-label="{{ cat.name }}"></a>
      <div class="card-content">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h2 class="card-title">{{ cat.name }}</h2>
          <span class="card-depth">{{ cat.depth }}</span>
        </div>
        <p class="card-excerpt">{{ cat.tagline }}</p>
      </div>
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</div>
